Review Text: Finest #mandi #khabsa #fahaam #arabicsweet @gachibowli.. clean and polite staff. Had amazing food.. looking forward for next visit with family and friends.

Cabrito's Mandi Rice tastes very good. I can relish it all by itself. I like their Faham Chicken. It's a barbecue item. The place is pretty and the carpet seating is the most comfortable area to chill out with friends while enjoying kabaabs.

The kebabs are brilliant here with the green chutney. The ambience is very good and restaurant is nice , finding a parking wasn't difficult.  The service is Excellent and food is delicious. A paradise for non-vegetarians - With good options for Vegetarians - 
Definitely recommend this place for quality and service !! Also try Baklava and Kunafa Dessert !!
